ation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","title":"MLNAnnotation","role":"symbol","type":"topic"}}}